{
  "texts": [
    "Our GPT industrial bot offers the following benefits over traditional smart dashboards and HMIs: • interactions: Unlike traditional implementing graphical interfaces, predefined visualizations, and numerical data to convey information that usually still rely on the operators' expertise to interpret them, the GPT industrial bot, thanks to the GPT-4 LM integrated, uses natural language processing (NLP) to carry human-like conversations.",
    "With this interaction format, it becomes easier for any operator (even those with less experience) to interact with the system and receive correctly all necessary information.",
    "• Integrated support and decision-making aid: The GPT industrial bot does not only monitor the production system to reflect hardcoded preprogrammed decisions like in most conventional HMIs but also analyses and adapts to different key features data changes to assist operators with the most suitable recommendations and decisionmaking based on the current circumstance (built upon the powerful GPT-4 LM).",
    "• Maintenance and troubleshooting tool: Contrasting traditional HMIs that usually analyze and limit themselves to presenting detected faults to operators for further actions, the GPT industrial bot can analyze and detect system faults, provide precise diagnostics, and dynamically identify potential causes and resolutions.",
    "• Synthetic data generator: The GPT industrial bot has an advanced feature, nonexistent in conventional dashboards and HMIs, to generate new data similar in format to the loaded factory information it received."
  ]
}